<div class="calendaria-release-message">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
      All current modules stay free — Patreon funds new premium modules, early access builds, and continued development.
      First 50 patrons at any tier earn a permanent @Founder role on Discord.
    </p>

    <p class="release-blurb">
      This is the biggest Calendaria update yet — a complete weather overhaul with wind, precipitation, forecasts,
      weather history, ambient sound, and a full PixiJS particle renderer powering 37 animated effects on the HUD. Huge
      thanks to <a href="https://www.patreon.com/cw/GambitsLounge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gambit</a> (FXMaster+
      developer) for collaborating on hand-crafted presets for all 40+ weather types.
    </p>

    <h4>Major Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Wind & Precipitation System</li>
      <li>Weather Inertia</li>
      <li>Weather History</li>
      <li>Forecast System</li>
      <li>Time-of-Day Color Shifting</li>
      <li>Moon Illumination</li>
      <li>HUD Weather Visuals</li>
      <li>FXMaster Integration</li>
      <li>Weather Ambient Sound</li>
      <li>Dome Below Bar option for HUD layout</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>17 new weather presets (Ice Storm, Monsoon, Sakura Bloom, Acid Rain, and more)</li>
      <li><code>/forecast</code> and <code>/weather</code> chat commands</li>
      <li>Weather Picker rebuilt</li>
      <li>Weather Editor for customizing visual properties of all weather types</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Too many to count!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="release-link" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
